## Windows Docker Desktop — Top Performance Fixes

### Fix 1: Bind Mount Slowness
Bind mounts cross the VM boundary on Docker Desktop — every file read is slow.

```yaml
# docker-compose.yml
services:
  web:
    volumes:
      - ./apps/web:/app:cached          # cached = host authoritative
      - /app/node_modules               # anonymous volume — stays in container
      - /app/.vite                      # Vite cache inside container
      - /app/dist                       # build output inside container

  api:
    volumes:
      - ./apps/api:/var/www/html:cached
      - /var/www/html/vendor            # vendor stays inside container
      - /var/www/html/storage
```

### Fix 2: .dockerignore — Create for Every Service

**Node.js / React:**
```
node_modules
.git
dist
build
.env*
coverage
